{"tid":1438203,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"振奮軍心，形勢大好，推呀","createTime":"2019-08-09T17:04:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-09T17:46:56.000Z","uid":151198,"like":16,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"f56c18986d4c7fa9789bc6d10944a6433c876650","tid":1438203,"uid":151198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:04:03.000Z","msg":"屌，最近有D標題post潑冷水 ，大家咪信，而家係形勢大好呀仆街。<br />\n簡單講幾點同大家振奮士氣，大家諗到其他既繼續接落去。<br />\n<br />\n1. 中美貿易戰，美國就算去到9月1號都係10%咋，仲有15%未出呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n2. 香港關係法傾緊啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n3. 瑞銀恐嚇緊中共呀屌你，如果中共武力對待，會公怖100位支那人既資產，有機會凍結堐tim呀屌你。仲未計美國、加拿大、巴拿馬、英國、澳洲、紐西蘭果d呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。<br />\n<br />\n4. 台灣大選啦，佢地而家要就住啦，唔可以太暴力啦，台灣睇緊啦。<br />\n<br />\n5. 機埸岩岩玩咋，已經好大效果，佢地緊加唔可以係果度武力驅散。<br />\n<br />\n6. 黑警們都無招啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，而家有毒催流淚氣體都得番過期果D，佢地緊加唔可以亂用。水炮車到而家都仲係靠嚇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />。起碼有兩個原因，第一，驚部車太易被人破壞，一出即玩完。第二，水炮車真係射死or射盲人到時會更會令民意爆騰，6月9號既武力鎮壓就係一個例子，同埋佢地開左潘朵拉盒子既話，黑警們應該以下自己收工既安全為優先<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n7.香港人好聰明，同一招唔會中2次，咩經濟牌大台分化左膠全部免疫，只須所有人貫徹1樣野，就係<span style=\"color: red;\">港共完成五大訴求先並滿意</span>先停止抗爭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n8. 香港人仲有好多招玩呀，狗共及權貴們。罷工熱身左1次咋，仲有罷課未玩，超守法 (舉報僭建、舉報地盤危險污水嘈音未玩呀)，仲有下次選舉可以用番狗共陰招，某派競選議員既Banner掛出街轉頭又唔見<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f5119aee5bb7e90d63620c729b839ec8dc9970e4","tid":1438203,"uid":151198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:06:21.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"7b7cff7019e3fb6eb77ce0c56e23e1b8ce643683","tid":1438203,"uid":151198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:06:52.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"247acfcb161de2c84d7c9259d788d1da4c5f49e2","tid":1438203,"uid":244133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:21.000Z","msg":"巴打唔好講晒啲黑魔法畀人聽先得架<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6bf6afaed87d4bec70d73e59572cdc4b1c0e0b27","tid":1438203,"uid":239453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:42.000Z","msg":"勿輕敵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a7c8e299c5819bb5fd3a861e7e7ae6128199b6dd","tid":1438203,"uid":229369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:07:43.000Z","msg":"武力鎮壓係612 ar<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a232876c1d1e5adbd21cde6dd12fca961c136972","tid":1438203,"uid":228092,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:08:53.000Z","msg":"阻一阻大家<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/moJ6sY2.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FmoJ6sY2.jpg&h=59f607b9&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WTmS7Y2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWTmS7Y2.png&h=67416cd3&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ctnbD5H.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FctnbD5H.jpg&h=1f1b63c8&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/zwVMsY3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FzwVMsY3.jpg&h=ac3691f6&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AuFgQco.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAuFgQco.jpg&h=b2911e63&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"e99d63dc06b3d8d55f6e5184112b6895e0c26f08","tid":1438203,"uid":151198,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:32:30.000Z","msg":"推呀"},{"pid":"cabf4118c4c359f2a19480981a61604b0b44b2f3","tid":1438203,"uid":275887,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-09T17:46:56.000Z","msg":